quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  28,1,"Ta'. Sin. Mim"
  28,2,"These are the verses of the Clear Book."
  28,3,"We recount to you with truth some parts of the story of Moses and Pharaoh for the benefit of those who believe.",footnotes:179949:1,footnotes:179950:2
  28,4,"Indeed Pharaoh transgressed in the land and divided its people into sections. One group of them he humiliated, and slew their sons and spared their daughters. Truly he was among the mischief-makers.",footnotes:179952:1,footnotes:179953:2,footnotes:179954:3
  28,5,"We wanted to bestow favour on those who were oppressed in the land. We wanted to make them leaders and heirs",footnotes:179955:1